1)    npm init -y

      npm i express nodemon sequelize mysql2

      npm i sequelize-cli

      npx sequelize-cli init

2) change config.json 
(change model index para config.js)

3) create .env

4) npx sequelize db:create

5) npx sequelize migration:generate --name ---
(crate migration(s))

6) npx sequelize db:migrate
(generate migration(s))

7) create models
(/models/Addresss.js - /models/Employee)

7) npx sequelize seed:generate --name ----
(create seeders to test)

8) npx sequelize db:seed:all
(execute seed)

9) create index.js (root)
(create server)


The tables association goes in the MODELS (Address/Employee)